Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露 给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.93,0:00:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是少主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:00:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮  少主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你已经像个妈妈一样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于被遗弃的婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子果然是部落长或是类似身份者的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你继续调查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总大将暂且不提  乌露特大姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我说得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也差不多该泡好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我要再泡一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  洗澡洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  今天就由神结来给他洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热水真舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东霞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芙芙  洗澡澡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒不舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东霞姐姐要不要也抱抱看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  吵吵闹闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我来陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你有趣的助兴节目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芙芙大便了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次换小便了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙米露露阁下  请等一下  请稍等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有准备啊  能给我一杯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人您来陪我么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  拜托你手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您喝得真大气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒一好喝  不注意就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要尝尝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  请用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露  睡觉时间到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  真遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露  这个是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得轻闲…喝点酒什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  差不多该结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露  拜托你给我拿杯水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾  艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露也快睡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿  阿露露  等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露  把阿露露…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖  不要哭  小芙芙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖  乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭？  小便？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是尿布湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我觉得是他想吃奶了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶  我去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:12:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  只有你们在么  艾露露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去山里割草了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  小芙芙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先帮他脱下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是温温的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉姐姐  你会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我记得一开始应该是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙米  妈妈回来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神结
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙米的尿布是你换的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是卡露拉姐姐换的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉换的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大概中午的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她来帮了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚月色也很美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你白天的时候帮忙照看那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:14:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  昨晚真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚你能陪我么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子需要母亲的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是共犯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被骂的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕艾露露么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  最怕艾伦加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}注：艾伦加据说是住在厕所里的瘟神。阿露露以此作为艾露露的绰号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确  艾伦加很可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很怕但是喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐生气是为了阿露露好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如不得不离开大家独自生活的话  你会怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  一家人要一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  一家人必须在一起的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅一下可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌露特莉阁下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东霞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙米露露确定是阿图族的少主和亚塔姆族的公主生下的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两部族长年对立  纷争不断
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎那个婴儿是不顾双方的反对生下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以为了让那孩子能平安地生活  大将让他们双方和解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天他们将准备来迎接那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么乌露特莉阁下会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌露特那边由我去说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对的是那个死脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:19:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人  多利前来参见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告  乌露特莉大人带着芙米露露逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的哦  不管发生什么  妈妈都会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌露特莉大人  请您回城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是结界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是平时的你  应该能注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱会令人盲目  像你这样的人竟然会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么有这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由你不是最清楚不过了么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那孩子还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌露特莉阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子是…  这孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌露特莉阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子的妈妈是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您住手  乌露特莉…阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌露特莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能别让我笑掉大牙？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所…干的事  和人贩子干的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是这孩子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人各有自己的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但应该是由各人自己决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拐走不懂事的婴儿的你  哪里算得上是妈妈了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  乌露特莉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会把这孩子交出去  不会交出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  不可以…用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.87,0:23:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌露特  卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.58,0:24:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起
